data.text:
Absolute distribution map for the name Kuhn

The surname Kuhn is the 1077. common name in Austria. The absolutely most people with this name can be found at the district Bezirk Wien (Stadt). In the district Bezirk Wien (Stadt) there a relativily the most people living with this name.

Maybe you are also interested in these spellings of the surname: Kühn, Kühner, Kühnl, Kuhner and Kuhnl
